    "heroDescription": "Tax practices manage complex seasonal workflows alongside year round document collection, client communication about return status, and appointment scheduling for reviews and consultations. When these functions operate in silos, tax season becomes a coordination nightmare. A bundled operational system ties your preparation workflow directly to document tracking, client updates, and scheduling so your team can focus on returns instead of logistics.",
